snippet.title: IQ Ball Walkthrough Cool Math Games
snippet.description: This is a physics puzzle in which you need to help the ball to collect all the targets, on each of the levels. The ball has a rope which it can cling to certain surfaces. From some surfaces it can be repelled with the help of a rope. In addition, you can pull up a small wooden object or something. The game is taken from the site Cool Math Games.
